<P>
BETTING WITH SURELOCK; 
</P>
<P>
THE SILICON SLEUTH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The grass proved greener for SURELOCK on the Del Mar turf last week. The 
computer's bets piled up the biggest bankroll ever in this friendly 
handicapping competition, dating through the Hollywood Park meeting. 
</P>
<P>
SURELOCK's bets for today are a $10 exacta box, Keep On Top-Crystal Bounty, in 
the third race; $40 to win and place on Desert Rumor and a $10 exacta box, 
Desert Rumor-Dirty Old Man-Front Line Ready, in the seventh race. 
</P>
