<HEADLINE>
<P>
MORNING REPORT: TV &amp; VIDEO 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By BETH KLEID, Arts and entertainment reports from The Times, national and 
international news services and the nation's press. 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Saddam's Life Story: Coming soon to your neighborhood video store, the Saddam 
Hussein story. On Sept. 14, Strand VCI Entertainment will release "Saddam 
Hussein -- Defying the World." The 30-minute documentary about the rise of the 
Iraqi leader sells for $9.98, and includes home-video footage of the Iraqi 
invasion into Kuwait as an added feature. BETH KLEID 
</P>
</TEXT>
