FOREIGN RELATIONS -- IRAQ; IRAQ -- ARMED FORCES -- KUWAIT; UNITED STATES -- 
ARMED FORCES -- SAUDI ARABIA; IRAQ -- FOREIGN POPULATIONS; KUWAIT -- FOREIGN 
POPULATIONS; AMERICANS -- IRAQ; AMERICANS -- KUWAIT; ANARCHY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
