BROADCASTS; NATIONAL FOOTBALL LEAGUE; CENSORSHIP 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA082290-0078 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 265382 </DOCID>
