STATES -- ECONOMY; UNITED STATES -- BUDGET; UNITED STATES -- INDUSTRY; IRAQ -- 
FOREIGN RELATIONS -- KUWAIT; MILITARY CONFRONTATIONS; PEACE; DEFENSE SPENDING; 
ECONOMIC FORECASTS 
</P>
